      "setup": "SAM ViT-B and MedSAM ViT-B were evaluated frozen through segment_anything SamPredictor. MedSAM used the official README-linked checkpoint with a local CPU-mapped copy because the original file is CUDA-serialized. Both models used identical label-derived bounding-box prompts for the TopCoW synthetic projection and the DIAS s40 sequence-level mask.",
